{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":695,"text":"When I was nine years old,"},{"time":2599,"text":"my mom asked me what I would want\nmy house to look like,"},{"time":6037,"text":"and I drew this fairy mushroom."},{"time":8520,"text":"And then she actually built it."},{"time":11794,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13791,"text":"I don't think I realized\nthis was so unusual at the time,"},{"time":16415,"text":"and maybe I still haven't,"},{"time":17947,"text":"because I'm still designing houses."},{"time":23325,"text":"This is a six-story bespoke home\non the island of Bali."},{"time":26698,"text":"It's built almost entirely from bamboo."},{"time":30360,"text":"The living room overlooks the valley\nfrom the fourth floor."},{"time":34967,"text":"You enter the house by a bridge."},{"time":38548,"text":"It can get hot in the tropics,"},{"time":40405,"text":"so we make big curving roofs\nto catch the breezes."},{"time":45760,"text":"But some rooms have tall windows\nto keep the air conditioning in"},{"time":49498,"text":"and the bugs out."},{"time":53515,"text":"This room we left open."},{"time":55233,"text":"We made an air-conditioned, tented bed."},{"time":58935,"text":"And one client wanted a TV room\nin the corner of her living room."},{"time":62569,"text":"Boxing off an area with tall walls\njust didn't feel right,"},{"time":66332,"text":"so instead, we made this giant woven pod."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72477,"text":"Now, we do have all the necessary\nluxuries, like bathrooms."},{"time":76630,"text":"This one is a basket\nin the corner of the living room,"},{"time":80999,"text":"and I've got tell you, some people\nactually hesitate to use it."},{"time":84513,"text":"We have not quite figured out\nour acoustic insulation."},{"time":87485,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":89923,"text":"So there are lots of things\nthat we're still working on,"},{"time":92500,"text":"but one thing I have learned\n"},{"time":94700,"text":"is that bamboo will treat you well\nif you use it right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98907,"text":"It's actually a wild grass."},{"time":100952,"text":"It grows on otherwise unproductive land --"},{"time":103924,"text":"deep ravines, mountainsides."},{"time":107267,"text":"It lives off of rainwater,\nspring water, sunlight,"},{"time":111493,"text":"and of the 1,450 species of bamboo\nthat grow across the world,"},{"time":116253,"text":"we use just seven of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118691,"text":"That's my dad."},{"time":120119,"text":"He's the one who got me\nbuilding with bamboo,"},{"time":122220,"text":"and he is standing in a clump"},{"time":124310,"text":"of Dendrocalamus asper niger\nthat he planted just seven years ago."},{"time":128327,"text":"Each year, it sends up\na new generation of shoots."},{"time":131369,"text":"That shoot, we watched it grow a meter\nin three days just last week,"},{"time":136143,"text":"so we're talking about sustainable\ntimber in three years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143225,"text":"Now, we harvest from hundreds\nof family-owned clumps."},{"time":146638,"text":"Betung, as we call it, it's really long,"},{"time":149290,"text":"up to 18 meters of usable length."},{"time":150956,"text":"Try getting that truck down the mountain."},{"time":153487,"text":"And it's strong: it has\nthe tensile strength of steel,"},{"time":157133,"text":"the compressive strength of concrete."},{"time":159849,"text":"Slam four tons straight down on a pole,"},{"time":162775,"text":"and it can take it."},{"time":165492,"text":"Because it's hollow, it's lightweight,"},{"time":168690,"text":"light enough to be lifted\nby just a few men,"},{"time":171410,"text":"or, apparently, one woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174130,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182279,"text":"And when my father\nbuilt Green School in Bali,"},{"time":186435,"text":"he chose bamboo for all\nof the buildings on campus,"},{"time":189639,"text":"because he saw it as a promise."},{"time":191892,"text":"It's a promise to the kids."},{"time":193796,"text":"It's one sustainable material\nthat they will not run out of."},{"time":198547,"text":"And when I first saw these structures\nunder construction about six years ago,"},{"time":202694,"text":"I just thought, this makes perfect sense."},{"time":206780,"text":"It is growing all around us."},{"time":208893,"text":"It's strong. It's elegant."},{"time":211283,"text":"It's earthquake-resistant."},{"time":213514,"text":"Why hasn't this happened sooner,\nand what can we do with it next?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217610,"text":"So along with some of\nthe original builders of Green School,"},{"time":222637,"text":"I founded Ibuku."},{"time":224613,"text":"Ibu means \"mother,\" and ku means \"mine,\"\nso it represents my Mother Earth,"},{"time":230271,"text":"and at Ibuku, we are a team\nof artisans, architects and designers,"},{"time":235363,"text":"and what we're doing together\nis creating a new way of building."},{"time":240316,"text":"Over the past five years together,"},{"time":242677,"text":"we have built over 50 unique structures,\nmost of them in Bali."},{"time":248737,"text":"Nine of them are at Green Village --"},{"time":251779,"text":"you've just seen inside\nsome of these homes --"},{"time":254612,"text":"and we fill them with bespoke furniture,"},{"time":258776,"text":"we surround them with veggie gardens,"},{"time":260834,"text":"we would love to invite you all\nto come visit someday."},{"time":263946,"text":"And while you're there,\nyou can also see Green School --"},{"time":266974,"text":"we keep building\nclassrooms there each year --"},{"time":269588,"text":"as well as an updated\nfairy mushroom house."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274548,"text":"We're also working on\na little house for export."},{"time":277938,"text":"This is a traditional Sumbanese home\nthat we replicated,"},{"time":281119,"text":"right down to the details and textiles."},{"time":285056,"text":"A restaurant\nwith an open-air kitchen."},{"time":289310,"text":"It looks a lot like a kitchen, right?"},{"time":292320,"text":"And a bridge that spans\n22 meters across a river."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297150,"text":"Now, what we're doing,\nit's not entirely new."},{"time":301691,"text":"From little huts to elaborate bridges\nlike this one in Java,"},{"time":306220,"text":"bamboo has been in use across\nthe tropical regions of the world"},{"time":309330,"text":"for literally tens of thousands of years."},{"time":312232,"text":"There are islands and even continents\nthat were first reached by bamboo rafts."},{"time":318290,"text":"But until recently,"},{"time":320823,"text":"it was almost impossible to reliably\nprotect bamboo from insects,"},{"time":325444,"text":"and so, just about everything\nthat was ever built out of bamboo is gone."},{"time":330613,"text":"Unprotected bamboo weathers."},{"time":332981,"text":"Untreated bamboo gets eaten to dust."},{"time":336371,"text":"And so that's why most people,\nespecially in Asia,"},{"time":339650,"text":"think that you couldn't be poor enough\nor rural enough to actually want"},{"time":343546,"text":"to live in a bamboo house."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346146,"text":"And so we thought,"},{"time":347981,"text":"what will it take to change their minds,"},{"time":350326,"text":"to convince people\nthat bamboo is worth building with,"},{"time":353507,"text":"much less worth aspiring to?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":356340,"text":"First, we needed safe treatment solutions."},{"time":359428,"text":"Borax is a natural salt."},{"time":361123,"text":"It turns bamboo into\na viable building material."},{"time":363839,"text":"Treat it properly, design it carefully,"},{"time":366602,"text":"and a bamboo structure\ncan last a lifetime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370390,"text":"Second, build something\nextraordinary out of it."},{"time":374148,"text":"Inspire people."},{"time":376240,"text":"Fortunately,"},{"time":377294,"text":"Balinese culture fosters craftsmanship."},{"time":379168,"text":"It values the artisan."},{"time":381143,"text":"So combine those\nwith the adventurous outliers"},{"time":383970,"text":"from new generations\nof locally trained architects"},{"time":387105,"text":"and designers and engineers,"},{"time":390530,"text":"and always remember that you are designing"},{"time":393683,"text":"for curving, tapering, hollow poles."},{"time":397451,"text":"No two poles alike, no straight lines,"},{"time":400725,"text":"no two-by-fours here."},{"time":403128,"text":"The tried-and-true, well-crafted formulas\nand vocabulary of architecture"},{"time":408109,"text":"do not apply here."},{"time":409427,"text":"We have had to invent our own rules."},{"time":411731,"text":"We ask the bamboo what it's good at,\nwhat it wants to become,"},{"time":416198,"text":"and what it says is: respect it,\ndesign for its strengths,"},{"time":420690,"text":"protect it from water,\nand to make the most of its curves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424435,"text":"So we design in real 3D,"},{"time":426336,"text":"making scale structural models"},{"time":428159,"text":"out of the same material\nthat we'll later use to build the house."},{"time":431258,"text":"And bamboo model-making, it's an art,"},{"time":433278,"text":"as well as some hardcore engineering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442752,"text":"So that's the blueprint of the house."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444632,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":447042,"text":"And we bring it to site,"},{"time":448951,"text":"and with tiny rulers,\nwe measure each pole,"},{"time":451691,"text":"and consider each curve, and we choose\na piece of bamboo from the pile"},{"time":456288,"text":"to replicate that house on site."}]},{"cues":[{"time":460064,"text":"When it comes down to the details,\nwe consider everything."},{"time":463417,"text":"Why are doors so often rectangular?"},{"time":465530,"text":"Why not round?"},{"time":466876,"text":"How could you make a door better?"},{"time":468523,"text":"Well, its hinges battle with gravity,"},{"time":470498,"text":"and gravity will always win in the end,"},{"time":472658,"text":"so why not have it pivot on the center"},{"time":475398,"text":"where it can stay balanced?"},{"time":477650,"text":"And while you're at it,\nwhy not doors shaped like teardrops?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":482316,"text":"To reap the selective benefits\nand work within the constraints"},{"time":485366,"text":"of this material,"},{"time":487100,"text":"we have really had to push ourselves,"},{"time":489329,"text":"and within that constraint,\nwe have found space for something new."},{"time":495235,"text":"It's a challenge: how\ndo you make a ceiling"},{"time":497525,"text":"if you don't have any\nflat boards to work with?"},{"time":500660,"text":"Let me tell you, sometimes I dream\nof sheet rock and plywood."},{"time":505210,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":507710,"text":"But if what you've got\nis skilled craftsmen"},{"time":511819,"text":"and itsy bitsy little splits,"},{"time":514490,"text":"weave that ceiling together,"},{"time":516672,"text":"stretch a canvas over it, lacquer it."},{"time":519635,"text":"How do you design durable\nkitchen countertops"},{"time":522352,"text":"that do justice to this curving\nstructure you've just built?"},{"time":525904,"text":"Slice up a boulder like a loaf of bread,"},{"time":528737,"text":"hand-carve each to fit the other,"},{"time":531106,"text":"leave the crusts on,"},{"time":533427,"text":"and what we're doing,\nit is almost entirely handmade."},{"time":537677,"text":"The structural connections\nof our buildings"},{"time":539813,"text":"are reinforced by steel joints, but we use\na lot of hand-whittled bamboo pins."},{"time":544695,"text":"There are thousands of pins in each floor."},{"time":548891,"text":"This floor is made of glossy\nand durable bamboo skin."},{"time":553883,"text":"You can feel the texture under bare feet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556995,"text":"And the floor that you walk on,"},{"time":559610,"text":"can it affect the way that you walk?"},{"time":561453,"text":"Can it change the footprint\nthat you'll ultimately leave on the world?"},{"time":566329,"text":"I remember being nine years old"},{"time":568279,"text":"and feeling wonder,"},{"time":570183,"text":"and possibility,"},{"time":572200,"text":"and a little bit of idealism."},{"time":574474,"text":"And we've got a really long way to go,"},{"time":577330,"text":"there's a lot left to learn,"},{"time":579732,"text":"but one thing I know is that\nwith creativity and commitment,"},{"time":584672,"text":"you can create beauty and comfort"},{"time":589223,"text":"and safety and even luxury"},{"time":592450,"text":"out of a material that will grow back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":595408,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597651,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}